HEADWORD: Noticeable
<hw>No"tice*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of being
observed; worthy of notice; likely to attract observation;
conspicuous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>noticeable</qex> man, with large gray eyes.</q>
<rj><qau>Wordsworth.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Noticeably</ent>⟦br⟧
